            <h4>Support For The Needy And Poor</h4>
            <p>
                Assisting the needy in society is one of the major objectives of Juliana’s Holistic healthcare Services.
                We recognize the difficulty many in the society face in trying to acquire certain basic yet very
                essential needs in life; shelter, food and clothes. Now as part of our humanitarian services, Juliana’s
                Holistic Healthcare Services will be undertaking evangelism missions and be making donations to needy
                ones in society; here we will visit orphanages in rural communities to make donations of clothes, food
                and some financial assistance.
            </p>
            <p>
