                with temporary accommodation. This will help them focus on how to increase their economic gains, since
                they will be provided with places to lay their heads and also keep their personal belongings, thereby
                speeding up the process of them finding their own homes, plus the added benefit of acquiring a
                vocational skill.
            </p>
